Package com.i2group.apollo.client

Contains interfaces and a class for interacting with i2 Analyze through the supplied Java client.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IClientFactory
    A factory for creating clients for the i2 Analyze web services.
    IDelpsServiceFacade
    A set of methods for interacting with an i2 Analyze DELPS (data load ELP stage) solution, including the ability to synchronize Items in the ELP stage with changing data in an external source.
    IDocumentDownloadServlet
    A method for downloading binary documents from the i2 Analyze document store.
    IDocumentUploadServlet
    A set of methods for uploading binary documents to the i2 Analyze document store.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientFactoryFactory
    A factory for creating IClientFactorys that in turn can create clients for i2 Analyze web services.

Package com.i2group.apollo.client Description

Contains interfaces and a class for interacting with i2 Analyze through the supplied Java client.
